{"tid":323154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【劉曉波病逝】當局證中午已海葬 大哥：感謝黨和政府","createTime":"2017-07-15T11:38:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-15T16:15:49.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"435492d5ab3f4666deb0779cbbf0272874ff0e34","tid":323154,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T11:38:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170715/large/1500108793_4006.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170715%2Flarge%2F1500108793_4006.jpg&h=4d5680c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170715/large/1500111292_b644.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170715%2Flarge%2F1500111292_b644.jpg&h=7b46130b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n諾貝爾和平獎得主劉曉波的遺體今早已於瀋陽市的殯儀館火化，當局下午4時45分再舉行記者會，並安排劉曉波的兄長劉曉光出席。當局稱劉曉波已於中午海葬。<br />\n<br />\n劉曉光在記者會上稱，他在遼寧瀋陽半個月，劉曉波被送院、搶救、火化及海葬的過程都有參與，他在記者會上「感謝黨和政府」，按家屬心願處理後事，他更稱當局「照顧周到，完美」，體現人道主義精神，完合出乎他的意料。<br />\n<br />\n劉曉光又指出，在這個過程中，「體現了我國社會主義優越性」，認為當局能整合全國、世界頂尖的肝癌專家，為劉曉波搶救。<br />\n<br />\n他又表示，在救治及身後事的過程，都是由他與劉曉波妻子劉霞共同決定，政府所作的處理方式，都是他與劉霞所提出來的要求，「政府一一圓滿兌現」。<br />\n綜合報道"},{"pid":"1ded7ed705f6476eedf735ff5a9147a4281c9ac8","tid":323154,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T14:32:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee7974e1844e61454b31ac04a47b8fce3a2a1121","tid":323154,"uid":31098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T15:59:01.000Z","msg":"應該都同銅鑼灣書店單嘢一樣手法啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲賤過以前 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b76ed33a69c720ecc0afc40faf381f0e4412e90","tid":323154,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-1